---
title: Chorizo and Potato Hash with parsley aioli
description: Golden roasted potatoes form the base of this wonderful jumble of a dish. Also making an appearance are smoky chorizo, juicy cherry tomatoes and zippy scallions for added crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221101_R02_W51_IE_IEXCP0153-4_MB_Main_high-7663a9ef.jpg
